    "description": "IMOD is a set of image processing, modeling and display programs used\nfor tomographic reconstruction and for 3D reconstruction of EM serial\nsections and optical sections. The package contains tools for assembling\nand aligning data within multiple types and sizes of image stacks,\nviewing 3-D data from any orientation, and modeling and display of the\nimage files.\n",
